  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 0</strong> Evocation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nFlame-like radiance descends on a creature that you can see within range. The target must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take 1d8 Radiant damage. The target gains no benefit from Half Cover|XPHB or Three-Quarters Cover|XPHB for this save.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 1d8 when you reach levels 5 (2d8), 11 (3d8), and 17 (4d8).</p>",
